= display_search_boxes('catalog')

.row
  .landing_main.col-sm-8

    .title Catalog

    = render partial: '/datasource_warning', locals: {warning: warning}

    %p Search Columbia's catalog of over 18 million items for:
    %ul
      %li books
      %li journals and newspaper titles
      %li audio and video recordings
      %li scores
      %li archival collections
      %li databases
      %li government documents
      %li maps and atlases

    %p From the results page, refine your search by any combination of format, publication date, author, library location, language, subject, recently added, or call number.  To view these options before searching, enter a blank search.

    %p To find individual articles, try our #{datasource_switch_link('articles', 'articles')} search


